34
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:51,420
[SPEAKER_10] Pa evo, ja sam to prebirao ovdje u svom srcu, šta sam čuo?

35
00:07:51,420 --> 00:07:55,519
[SPEAKER_10] A mislim da ću prebirati još danima koji slijede iza mene.

36
00:07:55,519 --> 00:07:57,500
